## Rules for All Agents
- Always read this file (CLAUDE.md) at the start of a task for current project context
- Never modify files outside your designated directories
- All changes require reviewer approval before being considered done
- Always run tests before AND after making changes
- Log every change in CHANGELOG.md with date, what changed, and measured impact
- Git checkpoint before every change, git commit after every approved change
- One focused change per cycle (don't rewrite everything at once)
- Agent improvement suggestions go to AGENT-IMPROVEMENTS.md under "Pending" — NOT in report footers, memory files, or inline comments

